    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Describes shipping with inland navigation vessels for the transportation of goods and people on rivers, lakes and other inland waterways. Inland navigation vessels are used to transport cargo from and to sea-going ships, but also for conveyance of goods and passengers between places that are connected by inland waterways.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
